{
  "stem": "1479.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even over there, I was very curious how the things are done.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And again, I was very obedient, following the orders.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And by doing so, I did avoid a lot of unpleasant things, even from the Nazis or the managers in-- in the factory.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It depends.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some were, really, there was no problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were just doing their work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But if a Nazi wanted to find something, they always managed to find something to make-- to cause problem.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in fact I had-- I myself, the quiet one, the bashful one-- I was in big-- in big trouble one day in Schindler's factory because, like I mentioned before, the Nazis never ceased.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They always were looking and finding something to degrade use.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One day they announced there will be no work, so we always lived in-- in fear.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we thought that we'll be deported, sent it away somewheres to the death camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "However, the reason for not going to work was different, rather simple, because the Nazis brought full trucks of the clothing, the striped uniforms-- maybe somebody who saw the movie or some books-- so they took everything away from us.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the only outfits we were given were the striped uniforms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Uniforms for the woman was one piece dress.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The men had a pair of pants and a jacket and even a hat to make you look more like not normal people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When they gave out those uniforms, and I brought the dress to my barrack, what I was shocked because they brought the dresses one size fits all.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And yet I was still a teenager.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was a very petite girl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I looked at it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was huge.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And without thinking-- you know, it was almost like rebelling.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
